headline: 3 Once-Promising Growth Stocks That Are Down 40% Since the 2020 Crash -- Can Any of Them Recover?
summary: It's been five years since the 2020 market crash, when news of a global pandemic sent investors into a panic.  For investors brave enough to buy amid that crash, the gains for many stocks have been significant since then.  It was on March 16, 2020, that many stocks hit their lows.
